  note_en = coalesce(nullif(note_en, ''), 'Source section: Miscellaneous
Source excerpt: We love the ease and adaptability of the Loop Switch 2 earplugs.
Price reference: Amazon/US reference: $59.95 | CN reference: ~CNY 432 (Taobao/Tmall search baseline)
Worth noting:
- We love the ease and adaptability of the Loop Switch 2 earplugs.
- The comfortable rubber tips let you either block out nighttime noise to sleep or protect your hearing in noisy situations like concerts and fireworks shows.
- They have three modes, just like your favorite earbuds: Quiet, Experience, and Engage, so you can choose your volume level in any setting with the manual dial, even while wearing them.'),
  note_zh = coalesce(nullif(note_zh, ''), '来源章节：Miscellaneous
原文摘录：We love the ease and adaptability of the Loop Switch 2 earplugs.
价格参考：海外参考：$59.95 | 国内参考：约￥432（淘宝/天猫检索基准）
值得关注：
- We love the ease and adaptability of the Loop Switch 2 earplugs.
- The comfortable rubber tips let you either block out nighttime noise to sleep or protect your hearing in noisy situations like concerts and fireworks shows.
- They have three modes, just like your favorite earbuds: Quiet, Experience, and Engage, so you can choose your volume level in any setting with the manual dial, even while wearing them.'),
  tags_zh = case when coalesce(array_length(tags_zh,1),0)=0 then ARRAY[]::text[] else tags_zh end,
  tags_en = case when coalesce(array_length(tags_en,1),0)=0 then ARRAY[]::text[] else tags_en end
where lower(coalesce(name_en, name, '')) = lower('Loop Switch 2');


